The <code><strong>class</strong></code> <a href="/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Global_attributes">global attribute</a> is a space-separated list of the case-sensitive classes of the element. Classes allow CSS and Javascript to select and access specific elements via the <a href="/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/Class_selectors">class selectors</a> or functions like the DOM method <a href="/en-US/docs/Web/API/Document/getElementsByClassName"><code>document.getElementsByClassName</code></a>.